window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The new waitress at the Savage Saints clubhouse is a pretty little package wrapped up in mysteries and filled with secrets. I can't explain the urge to protect her, to reveal whatever she's hiding, whatever is making her so afraid.</p> <p>Tessa doesn't trust easily, but I've always loved a challenge. I'll win her over one smile at a time, and then I'll find a way to keep her forever.</p> <p>When the truth finally comes out, I have a decision to make. Trust Tessa and risk losing everything I've worked for, or leave the only woman I've ever cared about for the good of the club.</p> <p>Time's running out, and so are my options. Should I trust my head or my heart?</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
